Ralph P. Scozzafava



Mr. Ralph P. Scozzafava is on the Board of Directors at Dean Foods Co. and Stage Stores, Inc. Mr. Scozzafava was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Furniture Brands International, Inc., Vice President-Worldwide Commercial Operations by William Wrigley Jr. Co., and Chief Executive Officer by Heritage Home Group LLC.



